high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room, then go to the bathtub, to your left, in the corner.
Pick up the sponge in the back of the bathtub.
Turn to the sink on your right.
Place the sponge in the sink, turn the water on, soak up some water with the sponge, turn the water off, and remove the sponge from the sink.
Turn back to the bath tub on your right.
Place the sponge back into the bathtub, to the right of the other sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet sponge in the bathtub.

high_descs: Walk to the tub on the other side of the room.
Pick up the sponge that's farthest away in the tub.
Turn around to face the sink.
Put the sponge inside of the sink, rinse the sponge off with water, pick the sponge up from the sink.
Turn around to face the tub again.
Place the sponge in the tub to the right of the other sponge.
anns.task_desc: To rinse off a sponge and put it in the tub.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the tub.
Pick up the right sponge in the tub.
Turn around, bring the sponge to the sink.
Wash the sponge in the sink.
Bring the cleaned sponge back to the tub behind you.
Put the sponge in the tub, right of the other sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned sponge in the tub.
